Package io.dvlopt.linux.epoll

Class EpollEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.dvlopt.linux.epoll.EpollEvent

  • public class EpollEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    An EpollEvent specifies the type of events the kernel should monitor, or did respond to, and allows the user to store some basic data such as a file descriptor and get it back later when an event occurs.
